# Colophon

This manual was typed in emacs, formatted using markdown and converted
to pdf, html, troff and latex using pandoc and pdflatex.

The complete source code to this manual is available in the 'doc'
directory of the Sassetti source distribution.

## Who was Sassetti?

[Francesco Sassetti](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Francesco_Sassetti)
was a 15th century Florentine banker noted by history more for the
honesty and accuracy of his books than the success of his banks.

Ledger is a great and accurate tool, but is a niche program.  This
Lisp wrapper for Ledger could only be of interest to an extremely
small subset of Ledger's already small audience.  Sassetti seemed like
an accurate, if not auspicious, fit.
